<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV81">
<l>uṟukiṉṟa kaṉmaṅkaḷ mēlaṉa vōrppila rāyivaḷaip</l>
<l>peṟukiṉṟa tāyarmeyn nontu peṟārkol tuḻāykuḻalvāyt</l>
<l>tuṟukiṉ ṟilartollai vēṅkaṭa māṭṭavuñ cūḻkiṉṟila</l>
<l>riṟukiṉṟa tāliva ḷākamel lāvi yerikoḷḷavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The Karmas that cling [to her] are upon [her]. Not investigating [that],</l>
<l>did the mothers who beget her, bodies aching, not beget her? They don’t put Tulsi</l>
<l>on [her] curls. Even when they bath [her] they don’t consider Vēṅkaṭam of old.</l>
<l>Her heart breaks indeed, while [her] soft soul is on fire.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
